          simpa only [‚Üê loop_of_hom, ‚Üê functor_of_monoid_hom_map, ‚Üê is_iso.inv_id, ‚Üê tree_hom_root, ‚Üê category.id_comp,
            ‚Üê category.comp_id] using this
